collection.name: Caked Apes Official
collection.description:
What happens when a group of apes working in a bakery gets pissed on by birds putting out a fire set by potatoes? Caked Apes happen. They are 8888 unique orphaned NFTs that need a home. Won't you please consider taking some Caked Apes home before they spoil?

[cakedapes.com](https://cakedapes.com)
